{"tid":591382,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[鋼之鍊金術師] 有冇手足會玩steam隻新game 叫My Lovely Daughter","createTime":"2018-03-13T13:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T08:14:31.000Z","uid":14719,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7db71fceca7776332d5cc33f7a51280b8b02ca9","tid":591382,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">My Lovely Daughter</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/15/203220_de3d03f4f76703e08bf1231f12465886.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F15%2F203220_de3d03f4f76703e08bf1231f12465886.png&h=8a23a0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介：<br />\n玩家將扮演一名失憶的父親浮士德，試圖通過灌注靈魂來讓自己毫無生氣的女兒重新復蘇。遊戲中需要購買基礎材料來煉成人偶（人造人，homunculus），讓人偶們在鎮子中工作來賺取金錢並提升她們靈魂的質量，並且在時機合適時通過殺死她們來獲取靈魂。<br />\n<br />\n隻game依家做緊9折 即係HK$68.40<br />\n<br />\n有冇鋼鍊撚想買黎做下鍊金術師 <br />\n懷念下當年哦呢醬嘅劇情"},{"pid":"de2e3a2440f960cf954fda3c094f0fb4d74af9c8","tid":591382,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0791d9b34910f41619bd3a7064d58e86d94aa4b7","tid":591382,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"睇到steam d留言已經嚇到瀨屎<br />\n精神獵奇"},{"pid":"d0693941b1c8e7a03f77249f149beb245da901a7","tid":591382,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0791d9b34910f41619bd3a7064d58e86d94aa4b7","tid":591382,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"睇到steam d留言已經嚇到瀨屎<br />\n精神獵奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:53:20.000Z","msg":"你平時都睇開架啦"},{"pid":"77fe7c2b38ddfe339a62af100390d9b8c976d1f2","tid":591382,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:25:31.000Z","msg":"good game ar"},{"pid":"20647d